# SOLANA MILLION DOLLAR GRID
## Whitepaper v1.1

**The World's First Interactive Blockchain Advertising Space on Solana**

---

## Abstract

Solana Million Dollar Grid (SMD) is a revolutionary blockchain-based advertising platform that transforms digital real estate into a permanent, tradeable asset on the Solana blockchain. Inspired by the legendary Million Dollar Homepage but enhanced with Web3 technology, SMD enables individuals and businesses to own a piece of internet history while benefiting from our planned token economy and expansion roadmap.

