## 4. Current Features

### âœ… Live Features (November 2024)

#### 4.1 Grid System
- **1000x1000 interactive grid** with real-time updates
- **Drag-and-drop selection** with visual feedback
- **Instant availability check** prevents double bookings
- **Zone-based pricing** with color-coded areas

#### 4.2 Wallet Integration
- **Phantom Wallet** support
- **Secure authentication** with cryptographic signatures
- **Balance checking** in real-time
- **Transaction verification** on-chain

#### 4.3 Payment System
- **SOL payments** directly to owner wallet
- **Instant confirmation** (~400ms on Solana)
- **Transaction tracking** with Solscan links
- **Automatic pixel reservation** after payment

#### 4.4 Media Upload
- **Logo upload** (PNG, JPG, GIF)
- **Automatic optimization** for grid display
- **URL linking** to your website
- **Project metadata** storage

#### 4.5 Admin Features
- **Owner-only access** with wallet verification
- **Delete capability** for emergencies
- **Real-time monitoring** of sales
- **Stats dashboard**

#### 4.6 Notifications
- **Telegram integration** for sale alerts
- **Transaction details** sent automatically
- **Project information** included

#### 4.7 Infrastructure
- **Helius RPC** for reliable Solana connection
- **Persistent storage** on Render.com
- **Automatic backups** of all data
- **99.9% uptime** guaranteed

